money here, there.

00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:29.510
But it's always good to
give the money on something

00:12:29.510 --> 00:12:33.022
you believe in, on something
that you're making sure

00:12:33.022 --> 00:12:34.730
that it is making a
difference, is having

00:12:34.730 --> 00:12:37.504
an impact on our
society, and that

00:12:37.504 --> 00:12:38.670
are becoming very important.

00:12:38.670 --> 00:12:41.460
I always tell all of my friends,
don't just give the money

00:12:41.460 --> 00:12:42.860
and run away.

00:12:42.860 --> 00:12:45.470
Give the money, but also want
to know where's your money's

00:12:45.470 --> 00:12:46.270
going.

00:12:46.270 --> 00:12:48.530
That's very important.

00:12:48.530 --> 00:12:53.080
I think for me, I knew where
I was giving my $25 million,

00:12:53.080 --> 00:12:56.740
where it was going, and what
was going to happen to it,

00:12:56.740 --> 00:13:00.847
how much difference my money
was going to make in society.

